<h2>Welcome to the travel bucket list</h2>

<p>Use this web application to record countries and cities you have visitied, and those still waiting on your bucket list!</p>

<div class="app-features">
<li>Track countries and cities you want to visit and have visited</li>
<li>Create and edit countries and cities</li>
<li>Each country can have one or more cities to visit</li>
<li>Mark destinations as visited or still to see</li>
</div>

